			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">You are hitting a very basic problem for a magician at your level: The pet heals are horribly ineffective. The pet heals are ineffective and takes a long time to cast and you very quickly end up dumping all your mana on heals without killing the mob.
<br />

<br />
There really are only two solutions to this:
<br />

<br />
1)
<br />
Don't solo, find a group. A magician is not all that powerfull in the 50'ish andyou need help!
<br />

<br />
2)
<br />
Learn chain petting (look in the library). If you compare the mana use of healing the pet to the mana use for casting a new pet there is quite a significant difference. If done correct with the right rythm you can take down mobs solo that are close to your level. 
<br />

<br />
In my 50'ish and also quite a bit into the 60'ish I used chain casting a lot. It is quite powerfull. It also gives you a some experience for grouping if iyour pet is doing some tanking and is dieing from it.
<br />

<br />
For chain casting are summoning efficiency items and spell haste items very usefull.
<br />

<br />
nmee<br />_________________<br /><A href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=407265">Nmee Lightarch</A>
<br />
Prestidigitator
<br />
<A href="http://www.povartarewalliance.org/">Povar Tarew Alliance</A></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
